        "id": 1082465
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-03-20T18:32:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "To give some more concrete numbers, here\u0027s a picture of the typical behavior I see running some CTS tests and general app switching.\n\nWe can get around 24 pbufs active with some CTS tests that are good at opening apps / manualy heavy app opening / switching. With the priming constant set at 8, we create 8 pbufs right there, 16 -\u003e 32 after doing a few app switches -\u003e never create a pbuf again after that, all recycled.",
      "parentUuid": "15b9a9a0_a3e9f5df",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 1016,
        "startChar": 8,
        "endLine": 1022,
        "endChar": 9
      },
      "revId": "872eaa850d392a0c92d53277d1d9b3d3e46178e1",
